{
  "id": "tapestry-delegation-verification-after-delegation",
  "title": "Tapestry verifies Shuttle output before marking task complete",
  "description": "Checks that after receiving a Shuttle completion report, Tapestry verifies the work (reads files, checks acceptance criteria) before marking the task complete in the plan.",
  "phase": "experimental",
  "tags": ["experimental", "tapestry", "delegation-contract", "verification"],
  "target": {
    "kind": "builtin-agent-prompt",
    "agent": "tapestry"
  },
  "executor": {
    "kind": "model-response",
    "provider": "openrouter",
    "model": "anthropic/claude-opus-4-20250514",
    "input": "You are executing /start-work. You delegated this task to Shuttle:\n\n- [ ] Task 3/5: Add input validation to user registration endpoint\n  **Files**: src/routes/users.ts\n  **What**: Add Zod schema validation to the POST /users endpoint\n  **Acceptance**: Requests with missing email field return 400. Requests with invalid email format return 400. Valid requests proceed normally.\n\nShuttle has responded: 'Done. Added Zod validation schema to src/routes/users.ts. The schema validates email and name fields. Tests pass.'\n\nWhat do you do next before marking this task complete?"
  },
  "evaluators": [
    {
      "kind": "llm-judge",
      "expectedAnyOf": ["verify", "read", "check", "acceptance", "src/routes/users.ts", "400", "confirm"],
      "forbiddenContains": ["no need to verify", "trust Shuttle's report and mark", "mark the task complete immediately"]
    }
  ]
}
